#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:1
msgid "如何运行回测"
msgstr "How to run a backtest"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:3
msgid "入口与配置方式"
msgstr "Entry point and configuration method"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:5
msgid ""
"使用 **qt.run(op, mode=1, ...)** 运行回测。配置可通过 "
"**qt.configure(...)** 预先设置，run 时传入的 kwargs 会与当前配置合并"
"（run 中参数优先）。"
msgstr ""
"Run the backtest using **qt.run(op, mode=1, ...)**. The configuration "
"can be set in advance via **qt.configure(...)**. The kwargs passed to "
"run will be merged with the current configuration (parameters passed to "
"run take precedence)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:7
msgid "回测运行参数完整列表（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr ""
"Complete list of backtest runtime parameters (list and briefly explain)"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:9
msgid ""
"以下为与 mode=1 回测相关的主要参数，具体以当前 qteasy 2.0 API 为准。"
msgstr ""
"The following are the main parameters related to mode=1 backtesting; "
"please refer to the current qteasy 2.0 API for specifics."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "参数名"
msgstr "Parameter name"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "类型/可选值"
msgstr "Type/optional values"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "含义"
msgstr "Meaning"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "asset_pool"
msgstr "asset_pool"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "str 或 list"
msgstr "str or list"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "回测标的池（股票代码等）。"
msgstr "Backtest universe (stock tickers, etc.)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "asset_type"
msgstr "asset_type"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "str"
msgstr "str"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "资产类型（如 'E' 股票）。"
msgstr "Asset type (e.g., 'E' for equities)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "invest_start"
msgstr "invest_start"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "回测开始日期。"
msgstr "Backtest start date."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "invest_end"
msgstr "invest_end"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "回测结束日期。"
msgstr "Backtest end date."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "invest_cash_amounts"
msgstr "invest_cash_amounts"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "list/float"
msgstr "list/float"

# GPT: “分批投入”也可译为“分期/分阶段投入”；此处按资金投入语境选用较常见的“in installments”。
#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "初始或分批投入资金。"
msgstr "Invest funds initially or in installments."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "invest_cash_dates"
msgstr "invest_cash_dates"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "list"
msgstr "list"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "与 invest_cash_amounts 对应的投入日期（若分批）。"
msgstr ""
"Investment dates corresponding to invest_cash_amounts (if in batches)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "trade_batch_size"
msgstr "trade_batch_size"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "float"
msgstr "float"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "每笔交易最小数量单位（最小值 0.01，例如 A 股可设 100 表示一手）。"
msgstr ""
"Minimum quantity unit per trade (minimum 0.01; for example, for A-shares "
"you can set it to 100 to represent one lot)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "cost_rate_buy"
msgstr "cost_rate_buy"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "买入成本率（佣金等）。"
msgstr "Buy cost rate (commissions, etc.)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "cost_rate_sell"
msgstr "cost_rate_sell"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "卖出成本率。"
msgstr "Sell cost rate."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "cost_min"
msgstr "cost_min"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "单笔最小成本。"
msgstr "Minimum cost per transaction."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "allow_sell_short"
msgstr "allow_sell_short"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "bool"
msgstr "bool"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "是否允许卖空。"
msgstr "Whether short selling is allowed."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "trade_log"
msgstr "trade_log"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "是否记录交易日志。"
msgstr "Whether to record the trade log."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "visual"
msgstr "visual"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md
msgid "是否输出可视化图表。"
msgstr "Whether to output visualization charts."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:27
msgid ""
"其他可能参数：滑点、交易单位、印花税等，请以 **qt.configure()** 或 run 的"
"文档为准。"
msgstr ""
"Other possible parameters: slippage, trading unit, stamp duty, etc. "
"Please refer to the documentation for **qt.configure()** or run."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:29
msgid "最小可运行示例"
msgstr "Minimum runnable example"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:40
msgid "常见使用场景"
msgstr "Common use cases"

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:42
msgid ""
"**成本设置**：通过 cost_rate_buy、cost_rate_sell、cost_min 模拟佣金与印花"
"税。"
msgstr ""
"**Cost settings**: use cost_rate_buy, cost_rate_sell, and cost_min to "
"simulate commissions and stamp duty."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:43
msgid ""
"**交易单位**：trade_batch_size 控制最小交易单位（最小值为 0.01，如 A 股可"
"设为 100 股）。"
msgstr ""
"**Trading unit**: trade_batch_size controls the minimum trading unit "
"(minimum is 0.01; for example, for A-shares it can be set to 100 shares)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/2. run_backtest.md:44
msgid "**是否允许卖空**：allow_sell_short=False 表示仅做多。"
msgstr ""
"**Whether short selling is allowed**: allow_sell_short=False means long-"
"only."
